42
00:04:20.885 --> 00:04:23.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
so share them with Shin
and have Yasu come over, too.

43
00:04:23.638 --> 00:04:25.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I’ll tell him to drop by
on his way back from work.

44
00:04:25.807 --> 00:04:27.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
