to Misato while we’re at it.

47
00:04:31.187 --> 00:04:34.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Do as you wish. I’ve got work tonight,

48
00:04:34.524 --> 00:04:35.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
