<i>I’m the one</i>
<i>who’s taking advantage of Takumi,</i>

63
00:05:29.579 --> 00:05:33.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>using him as a man who will hold me</i>
<i>whenever I feel lonely.</i>

64
00:05:50.600 --> 00:05:51.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I don’t want it.

65
00:05:57.899 --> 00:06:00.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I said I don’t want it!

66
