because you gave me too much last time!

67
00:06:03.404 --> 00:06:08.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Then you can take this
as an advance payment for the next time.

68
00:06:36.229 --> 00:06:39.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
