so I purposely told you an earlier time.

70
00:06:42.568 --> 00:06:44.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So not to worry.

71
00:06:44.320 --> 00:06:45.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I brought you a change of clothes.

72
00:06:45.988 --> 00:06:47.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh, thanks.

73
00:06:47.115 --> 00:06:47.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I’ll put them here,

74
00:06:48.074 --> 00:06:51.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
so get ready while I go
and get Reira checked out.

75
00:06:51.828 --> 00:06:54.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
