You have a cold?

77
00:06:59.293 --> 00:07:02.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No, no. I just got carsick.

78
00:07:02.213 --> 00:07:06.092 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But I’ve never known you
to have motion sickness before.

79
00:07:06.175 --> 00:07:08.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Are you worried?
-Of course.

80
00:07:08.803 --> 00:07:12.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If you break down,
our entire band comes to a stop.

81
00:07:13.057 --> 00:07:15.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You’ll cause problems for everyone.
Don’t forget to oil the joints.

82
00:07:16.060 --> 00:07:18.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Don’t talk about me like I'm some object!

83
00:07:19.147 --> 00:07:23.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's just a figure of speech.
Then I’ll drink it myself.

84
