TO NANA KOMATSU
FROM SEIICHI AND HARUE MIZUKOSHI

92
00:07:47.300 --> 00:07:49.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>No way! From Mr. Mizukoshi? What is it?</i>

93
00:07:49.677 --> 00:07:51.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
WE GOT MARRIED

94
00:07:52.054 --> 00:07:54.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>He didn’t have to notify me about that.</i>

95
00:07:55.975 --> 00:07:58.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>That’s so nice. I envy them.</i>

96
00:07:58.936 --> 00:08:02.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>I wanna hurry and get married, too.</i>
<i>His wife is so cute.</i>

97
00:08:03.191 --> 00:08:05.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>He said he knew her since they were kids.</i>

98
00:08:05.234 --> 00:08:08.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I want a cool childhood friend, too.</i>

99
00:08:09.363 --> 00:08:12.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I don’t care if I don’t find</i>
<i>a rewarding job.</i>

100
00:08:12.742 --> 00:08:16.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>If I could just cook every day</i>
<i>for someone I love,</i>

101
00:08:16.287 --> 00:08:20.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>that'd make me so happy.</i>

102
00:08:21.209 --> 00:08:24.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>But marriage is unthinkable with Takumi.</i>

103
00:08:24.462 --> 00:08:27.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I should hurry up and put an end</i>
<i>to this pathetic relationship</i>

104
00:08:27.340 --> 00:08:29.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>and start a real one.</i>

105
00:08:29.800 --> 00:08:32.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>But can a person like me find someone</i>

106
00:08:32.261 --> 00:08:35.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>who will love me for the rest of my life?</i>

107
00:08:37.266 --> 00:08:40.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>What if things keep going like this</i>
<i>and I can't find anything to live for?</i>

108
00:08:40.353 --> 00:08:43.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Am I gonna grow old and die alone?</i>

109
00:08:45.816 --> 00:08:48.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Welcome home, Ms. Hachiko!
Everyone’s been waiting for you!

110
00:08:48.819 --> 00:08:50.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Huh?
-We’re celebrating.

111
00:08:50.196 --> 00:08:52.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
