136
00:10:10.401 --> 00:10:13.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
our queen, for one,
is feeling a sense of urgency,

137
00:10:13.613 --> 00:10:14.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and I had initially thought
if we’re gonna do this anyway,

138
00:10:14.864 --> 00:10:16.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
